{"tid":1874159,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」係無用架，淨化facebook行動 每日一更","createTime":"2020-02-11T04:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T11:22:02.000Z","uid":89974,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67ae0cdc4a929271e252bff311da15bf6f554f2c","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」<br />\n<br />\nFb好多呢種留句言就當做咗野嘅人，以蘋果/立場新聞及眾多群組為甚。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係同路人，但呢種心態其實係極懦弱同完全被動，我地唔可以令呢種風氣係示威者入面蔓延，否則個個都變哂等運到。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該鼓勵示威者更加進取咁行動，所以現正呼籲所有連登巴絲，舉行<span style=\"color: red;\">由今日起直到下星期日</span>嘅Facebook 淨化活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">目標：蘋果，立場所有的post<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1.每一次你見到有人留言「黑警死全家」「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」等回應時，用以下template回應佢(留意唔好短時間番太多次，會俾FB當係spam，想自己改下字眼都得)：</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;template&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n好人不長命，禍害遺千年，剩係靠許願係令唔到黑警暴斃，但我地一齊合力係可以架。<br />\n你可唔可以應承我同我一齊做以下至少一樣野？<br />\n<br />\n罷工 （要脅政府）<br />\n罷稅（斷狗糧）<br />\n杯葛黑警，斷絕社會關係<br />\n參加每一次黃陣營舉辦嘅活動，官方/非官方都去<br />\n杯葛藍絲，斷絕社會關係<br />\n有口罩俾手足唔好俾廢老藍絲<br />\n每日盡量去法院聲援被捕手足<br />\n每日發文宣俾朋友<br />\n試用Twitter<br />\n出街時貼memo紙係街邊做流動文宣<br />\n金錢支援手足<br />\n捐錢俾612<br />\n<br />\n杯葛藍店支持黃店（hktvmall 取代惠康華潤，唔食大家樂元氣）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你認同我地的話，下次見到有其他人留黑警死全家等回應時，請複製貼上此回覆！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;template&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">2.如果覺得template太長，可以用呢張代替</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RT622Zm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRT622Zm.jpg&h=116eabb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">3.每見到一個合資格嘅人選都留言一次，如果有人已經留咁嘅話就用like推佢前啲</span>"},{"pid":"7c8d57b8277a525dfe508941929ae663d4613fdc","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1015b974e2702a206ebd32c2bb20be52583eb76","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21567f0752d3c44f6ef1f17cd6c30d263d48c608","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcf7df22677e67fbf08b694b6d9f0402d1acd66","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178c81ba272279af5fccb3bd00c7545c6ec2b411","tid":1874159,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"edf94f5bef2a764de80ba196096263d61d117e4d","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea9c4a618b7a5dc14ee5bce107a3d7cb61ca504","tid":1874159,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd31ae4cf0b19912e52d5b6c7f9d4910d8968c8d","tid":1874159,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"986e2363e0095fada7c1a784e99a39a2308e47ff","tid":1874159,"uid":296705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}